Testes : Drogo pres- biter de Sancto Nicliolao, Hademarus presbiter de Pont Erchen- fredi, willelmus del Noiher, Tigerius de Pont Erclienfredi, Hive- linus ejus pater, Witalis homo Tigerii‚ Isernbardus senescalcus, Raynerius semeso-als, Ernegisus lilius Borel, Rotbertus de Vuar- leinvilla, Ricardus marescalcus, Haymericus filius Marses, Ray- naldus de Nigra Aqua, Godefridus sanguinator.
